dct_title_s: Plan of Proposed Passaic Lake Designed for Flood Control, Economic Utilization of the Passaic River and Sanitation of the Channel of the Lower Passaic
dct_description_sm: Map is a geological survey of NJ to accompany report. The map features various rivers labeled, profiles of elevation, high water line of the Passaic, Whippany and the dam at Little Falls.
